# ECSF-RFP-2022-1691: Project Management Services

## Government Tender Notice Cancelled

### Notice Type and Category

*   **Notice Type**: Request for Proposal (Demande de propositions)
*   **Procurement Category**: (civiL Service) SRV (Service Public)

### Tender Status

*   **Tender Status**: Cancelled (Annulé)

### Details of the Cancelled Tender

The tender announcement for the procurement of Project Management Services (Service de gestion de projets) under the Solicitation Number ECSF-RFP-2022-1691 was initially published on December 13, 2022. The tender was scheduled to close on December 20, 2022, at 02:00:00 hours.

### Key Stakeholders

*   **Contracting Entity**: Elections Canada (Élections Canada)
*   **End User Entities**: Elections Canada
*   **Contact Person**: Sufia Fuentes, Senior Advisor, Procurement and Contracting Services (Conseillère principale, Services de l’approvisionnement et des contrats)
*   **Contact Information**: proposition-proposal@elections.ca, 873-415-0446

### Address of the Contracting Entity

Elections Canada
30 Victoria Street, 1st Floor (Business Centre)
Gatineau, QC K1A 0M6
Attention: Sufia Fuentes, Senior Advisor, Procurement and Contracting Services
Elections Canada File No.: ECSF-RFP-2022-1691
Please note that the cancellation of the tender notice does not affect any provisional procedures in force. For any further inquiries, please contact the contracting entity.
